Processes features of layer whose geometries would intersect rectangle passed as param by calling visitor's visit method. FIXME FeatureVisitor is designed to work with memory and file drivers (visit(IGeometry, index), and to work with geometries (thats the reason for not to create Values, instead of pass an index) But DBDrivers recovers IGeometry and Values in dbAdapter.getFeatureIterator method. We must add a visit(Feature) method to FeatureVisitor.
